Title: The One-Loop Divergences of the Linear Gravity with the Torsion Terms

Authors: M.Yu.Kalmykov and P.I.Pronin

Comments: 13 pages in LATEX. (The title and references are changed. The

discussion of the BRST-symmetry added.)Journal-ref: Gen.Rel.Grav. 27 (1995) 873-886

We investigate the role of the torsion field at the quantum level in theaffine-metric theory of gravity. One-loop counterterms are calculated in thetheory with terms quadratic in the torsion field.